    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1772223804\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1772223804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1772223804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/ee68828abebb27be08759a6ea1f6f4ec.avif?t=1772223804\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接 Megabattle！这是一款 roguelike 卡牌游戏，将策略性的卡组构筑与史诗级机器人对战的刺激感融为一体。打造专属卡组，踏上程序生成的旅程，迎战越来越严苛的试炼。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/024dd0839fcf7d749ea147978a149b60.poster.avif?t=1772223804\" width=1038 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/024dd0839fcf7d749ea147978a149b60.webm?t=1772223804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/024dd0839fcf7d749ea147978a149b60.mp4?t=1772223804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Megabattle 中，每一次胜利都会带来宝贵奖励，包括零件与升级卡牌。利用这些资源强化你的卡组，让机器人更强大、更耐打。战斗时，合理出牌来强化部件、攻击对手，并抵御敌人的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/b9e9090e165ff8d5ce6c43342859cba6.poster.avif?t=1772223804\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/b9e9090e165ff8d5ce6c43342859cba6.webm?t=1772223804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/b9e9090e165ff8d5ce6c43342859cba6.mp4?t=1772223804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多种机器人职业，每种职业都有独特特性与可获取的部件。发现新的攻击卡牌与专属强化道具，壮大你的武装，并适应不同的战斗策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/cb53409cedbcdfbdb096fba28ce53d64.avif?t=1772223804\" width=1148 height=644 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式的科幻/未来氛围将带你进入一个充满机器人、先进科技与畅快动作的宇宙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整装待发，投入战斗，在 Megabattle 中夺取胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602030/extras/9c5b370bed1883836f32d33302810db6.avif?t=1772223804\" width=792 height=1080 /></span></p>",
